); font-size: 16.36px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 宋体; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">2、部分笔画与身份证的字交叉或接触。</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16.36px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 宋体; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">3、每一行后面一定要划上横线，以免被偷加其它文字。</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16.36px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 宋体; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">4、上述文字一定要签在身份证的范围内，但不要遮住(身份证上的姓名、文字及号码)。</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16.36px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 宋体; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">无论是信用卡、基金、手机、申请书，只要须附身份证复印件的，或填写和身份证有类似作用的表格，一律照此办理。另外，对各类申请书内尚未填写的空格，如：附卡申请，加买保险，加买第二支基金，申请手机号等等，这些空格都必须打上，以免被不法业者补填它用。</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16.36px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16.36px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 宋体; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">这个真的是非常重要，如果你学习过相关法律课程或票据课程你就知道，所以大家一定要十分小心点，在身份证复印件上千万记得要签名哟！</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16.36px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 宋体; line-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16.36px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 宋体; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">兹提供生活上便利的小方法保障自已的权利，你拿身份证复印件去办信用卡，记得在复印件上写：[此身份证复印件，仅为申请XX银行XX信用卡用，不得转为其它用途]。XXX签名。</span></strong></p>','[weixin]http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/OMdbYclvCbuZiaJtOpHRZAQcnnuqpaSD5dOobngaU8Rib5CoUWJVwAdzPaQAOvjeib3nKOTBqnAicpOmzmVDWA5fog/0?wx_fmt=jpeg','34','50','','0.05','2015-8-05');");
